        "text": "Thus saith the Lord - Or, יהוה yehovâh. Zedekiah lays aside the unmeaningful \"Lord\" אדני  'ǎdonāy of the general company of Israelite prophets 1 Kings 22:6, and professes to have a direct message from Yahweh to Ahab. He may have believed his own words, for the \"lying spirit\" 1 Kings 22:22 may have seemed to him a messenger from Yahweh. All the rest followed his example 1 Kings 22:12. ",
