        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "horns of Iron",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " [Thenius understands that these were iron spikes held on the forehead. But the reference is clearly to the horns of a bullock, and the appropriateness of the prophetic act is only manifest when we remember that Ephraim is compared to a bullock (",
        "children": []
      },
