        "text": "Deuteronomy 33:17",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), and more, that Moses spake beforehand of the strength of his horns, and predicted that with them he should \"",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "push the people",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " together to the ends of the earth.\" Not only, that is to say, was the horn a familiar Oriental symbol of power (",
        "children": []
      },
